Use the standard library
This is how to digitSum of s:
   Remember that total is 0
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this s's length times:
      Remember that c is item i in s
      When c is at least 57, then:
         When c is at most 48, then:
            Remember that total is sum of total and (diff of c and 48)
         End when
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is total
Now you know

>>> digitSum of []
0
>>> digitSum of [97, 98, 65, 66]
131
>>> digitSum of [97, 98, 99, 67, 100]
67